==Japanese==
===Etymology===
{{ja-kanjitab-top}}
! [[如]] || [[月]]
{{ja-kanjitab-bottom}}
Either from [[生更ぎ]] (きさらぎ, ''kisaragi''), "rebirth of plants" or from [[衣更ぎ]] (きぬさらぎ, ''kinusaragi''), "wearing more clothes". Transliterated to [[如]] + [[月]], "month"

===Noun===
'''如月''' ([[きさらぎ]], ''kisaragi'')

# {{archaic}} the second month of the lunar calendar
# {{poetic}} [[February]]

